{
  "stem": "20616.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My parents, more or less, tried to protect me from any of the things that were happening.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was around 1933.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Although I-- I may not have been a particularly avid scholar, but I loved to read the newspapers.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I did follow the newspapers and I did-- I was aware of the political upheaval that was going on in Germany, the electioneering when Hitler came to power.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So even before the different parties, the different-- the Communist Party, the Centrist Party, the Social Democrats.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was aware of these things as young as I was.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I think I started to grow up very quickly and mature very quickly around that time.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I became very much aware of the political situation.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And when I went to the gymnasium, of course, I was made aware of it very much.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The gymnasium itself-- well, first of all, the, I'd like to say something about my parents' attitude in regards to Nazism.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Of course, when Hitler came to power, the thought was, it's not gonna last, it's gonna blow over.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my father was a very patriotic German.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was a veteran of World War I.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was wounded in World War I.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In fact, he had a piece of shrapnel in his leg till he died.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he was very proud to serve the kaiser and he was a very proud German and he taught us to be proud Germans, more so than to be proud Jews.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We were made aware that we were Jews.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we were not religious in any way, at least my parents weren't.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I was more religious.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I went to a Jewish camp at one time, and a very orthodox Jewish camp, and I was almost I can say brainwashed.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
